title : Introduction_3
---
Juan: If you forget something, you can always review the contents of my order.
Juan: Anyway, tanda mo ga kung paano gumawa ng Lomi?

Protagonist: Well.... A basic lomi is compromised of three main parts...

<<declare $lomi_quiz = 0 as number>>
-> The Broth, the Noodles, and the Toppings.
    <<set $lomi_quiz = 1>>
-> The Soup, The Egg and The Kikiam
    <<set $lomi_quiz = 2>>

<<if $lomi_quiz == 1>>
Juan: Tama!
<<else>>
Juan: Too close! Pero eto talaga dapat 'yon.
<<endif>>

Juan: A lomi dish is composed of three main parts, The thick slimy broth, the starchy noodles and my favorite... tasty toppings!
Juan: Before anything else... let's make the broth!
Juan: First, drag the pot into the water to add water...
Juan: Turn up the stove to let the broth boil in low heat...
Juan: And drag some bones into the pot.
Protagonist: Bones...?
Juan: Yes! Traditionally, ginagamit talaga ang buto sa paggawa ng pork or beef stock.
Juan: If you run out of bones, you can always use bullion or pork or beef cubes as substitute!
Juan: Since mukhang magbubukas ka na mamaya. It also works in a time pinch. Since pork stock takes a while to boil!
Juan: After a while, season the water with salt and pepper. Optionally, you can also add onions!
Juan: This broth will be the foundation of a lomi's unique flavor, so make sure to prepare it properly!
===

