Juan: Now that our broth is secured, it's time to cook our noodles!
Juan: First, turn the wok's stove on...
Juan: Heat some oil at the stove...
Juan: Then sautee some onion and garlic...
Juan: After that, add the broth...
Juan: Cook the noodles...
Juan: ...And remember to add soy sauce to give it its distinct color!
